<plot>Perry Carlyle is torn between two women, the decent Anna Gray and the unprincipled Ruth Jordon. Perry works at the Treasury Department, and there he comes up with a scheme for passing off discarded mutilated bills as good currency. When the law catches onto his crime, he learns which of the women truly cares for him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?571465</url></doc>
